[{"id":"VH917809","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A curve in the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x y\"><math alttext=\"x y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>-plane is defined by the equation <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x cubed, plus y squared, minus 12 x, plus 16 y, equals 28 \"><math alttext=\"x cubed, plus y squared, minus 12 x, plus 16 y, equals 28 \" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><msup><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>16</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>28</mn></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. Which of the following statements are true?</p><ol class=\"ordered_list style:1\"><li class=\"list_paragraph\">At points where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x equals, negative 2\"><math alttext=\"x equals, negative 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, the lines tangent to the curve are horizontal.</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">At points where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y equals, negative 8\"><math alttext=\"y equals, negative 8\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, the lines tangent to the curve are vertical.</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">The line tangent to the curve at the point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"with coordinates negative 1, comma 1\"><math alttext=\"with coordinates negative 1, comma 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> has slope <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"one half\"><math alttext=\"one half\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</li></ol>\n","rubricRef":"VH917809_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">I and II only</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">II and III only</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">I and III only</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">I, II, and III</p>"],"answer":3}]